metadata.name: New Levels (A Film By Zora) 1
metadata.description:
A short film, produced in collaboration with Zora, showing a sneak peak into the creative process of multidisciplinary
 artist Brittany Pierre.

Brittany Pierre began her journey in web3 after seeing one of her favorite artists Elise Swopes success and dove straight in. Photography being her main medium, Brittany began to see success and make a name for herself in the space.

With the support of collectors and other artists in the space, 2023 began a new search for artistic expression. Through 3D animation, ai, photography, and music production, Brittany has begun to expand their artistic expression in the space.

As an NFTNow 100 artist for 2 years, Brittany also advocates for Black, POC and queer artists and hopes to see a more equitable web3 through curation, opportunities and advocacy.

*please ignore the corgi glitter (fur) on my couch. Idris and I were tussling cuz he likes to be center of attention. If you've been in a space with me, you know.
